Communication Packet format

From Raspberry pi to Arduino
  <X><Y><Z>

Wake up: 
  <1>

  <2><X>
  
Motion:
  <3><XY>
  X : U for Tilt Up
      D for Tilt Down
      N for no movement
      
  Y : R for Pan Right
      L for Pan Left
      N for no movement
  
Examples:
  <3><UL>   : for moving arm up and left
  <3><NR>   : for moving only right
  
  
